                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14957305" author="pauloricardomg" created="Wed, 14 Oct 2015 17:17:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;By default the hints directory is not specified, so the default hints directory is &lt;tt&gt;$cassandra_storagedir/hints&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On tarball installs, this variable is defined on &lt;tt&gt;bin/cassandra.in.sh&lt;/tt&gt;, but it&apos;s not defined on &lt;tt&gt;debian/cassandra.in.sh&lt;/tt&gt; for packaged installs. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Simple fix is basically to define &lt;tt&gt;$cassandra_storagedir=/var/lib/cassandra&lt;/tt&gt; on &lt;tt&gt;debian/cassandra.in.sh&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14957307" author="pauloricardomg" created="Wed, 14 Oct 2015 17:18:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After the fix, the hints directory is correctly created during first initialization on &lt;tt&gt;/var/lib/cassandra/hints&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14957364" author="pauloricardomg" created="Wed, 14 Oct 2015 17:41:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Mind reviewing &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=iamaleksey&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;iamaleksey&quot;&gt;iamaleksey&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14959731" author="iamaleksey" created="Thu, 15 Oct 2015 22:15:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed as &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/c3b2aedfd8bfce193abc8ed3809a850e603361d5&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;c3b2aedfd8bfce193abc8ed3809a850e603361d5&lt;/a&gt; to 3.0 and merged with trunk, thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
